{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Build a full-width hero section where all content is constrained to the theme’s inherent max-width container (do not break out of the max width for text or UI).
    Layout
    Two-column layout inside the max-width container
    Left column: text, icons, buttons
    Right column: a single full-height image that fills the column vertically
    Maintain strong spacing and hierarchy for desktop, tablet, and mobile
    Stack columns vertically on mobile (image below content)
    Left Column Content
    Large bold headline:
    “DTF Transfers Trusted by 225,000+” followed by a highlighted word that rotates
    The rotating word:
    Cycles through 5 different words
    Changes every 3 seconds
    Each word swaps to a new color
    Smooth fade or slide animation (no flashing)
    Supporting paragraph text below the headline
    Feature Rows
    Three horizontal feature items
    Each feature includes:
    A small square image icon (image block, not CSS shapes)
    A short line of text
    CTA Buttons
    Two primary CTA buttons side-by-side
    Clear visual contrast from background
    Stack vertically on mobile
    Bottom Info Blocks
    Two small content blocks beneath the buttons
    Each block contains:
    A square image icon
    A bold label
    One supporting line of text
    Right Column Image
    Single image
    Fills the full height of the section
    Covers the container with no distortion
    Crops responsibly on smaller screens
    General Requirements
    All red elements in the design are images, not CSS shapes
    Use image pickers for every icon or visual element
    Use semantic HTML
    Accessible color contrast
    No content exceeds the theme’s max width
    Section settings should allow:
    Editing all text
    Swapping images
    Changing rotating words and colors
    Animation
    Rotating word uses JavaScript or CSS animation
    3-second interval
    Infinite loop
    Smooth transitions only, feature icon and text should be 8px from one another, all features should bo on the same line with space in between. all text needs weight options and desktop and mobile size options., all content on the left needs a max width and image should take up all available width, image need to be container by width and aligned to bottom of section, left column needs bottom padding , section needs top padding and section needs bg color , need options for space between image and content for desktop and mobile, image needs to take up all available width Content max width leaves behind , image needs be contained by width , on desktop change split to a percent. when one changes have the other take the available space , make content width a percent and have image take up remaining width , make buttons follow the same rules and add spacing below them. , Content should always align vertically and have top and bottom padding for desktop and mobile , top and bottom padding should apply to content only  , image should be aligned to the bottom of the section. get rid of section top and bottom padding. button 1 and button 2 should run off the same style, Content (left section needs to always align to center of section horizontally , all content on the left needs to be left aligned. but the containers need to be center vertcailly in section, for layout "Content" needs to always be vertically aligned center , stack features on mobile with 8px between them. and on mobile put info blocks next to one another. add icon size for desktop and mobile  , get rid of button outlines and add spacing option below buttons for desktop and mobile , left section needs horizontal padding so it does not touch side of screen 
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.section_bg_color }};
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-hero-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ settings.theme_max_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: {{ block.settings.content_image_gap_desktop }}px;
  }

  .ai-hero-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: {{ block.settings.content_width }}%;
    max-width: {{ block.settings.content_max_width }}px;
    padding-top: {{ block.settings.content_padding_top_desktop }}px;
    padding-bottom: {{ block.settings.content_padding_bottom_desktop }}px;
    padding-left: {{ block.settings.content_padding_horizontal_desktop }}px;
    padding-right: {{ block.settings.content_padding_horizontal_desktop }}px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ai-hero-content-inner-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: left;
  }

  .ai-hero-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: calc(100% - {{ block.settings.content_width }}%);
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    align-self: stretch;
  }

  .ai-hero-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-hero-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .ai-hero-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    max-width: 500px;
    max-height: 500px;
  }

  .ai-hero-headline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.headline_size_desktop }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.headline_weight }};
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.headline_spacing }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.headline_color }};
  }

  .ai-hero-rotating-word-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-block;
    position: relative;
  }

  .ai-hero-word-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.5s ease-in-out;
  }

  .ai-hero-word-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active {
    position: relative;
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .ai-hero-paragraph-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.paragraph_size_desktop }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.paragraph_weight }};
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.paragraph_spacing }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.paragraph_color }};
  }

  .ai-hero-features-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: {{ block.settings.features_gap }}px;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.features_spacing }}px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .ai-hero-feature-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .ai-hero-feature-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: {{ block.settings.feature_icon_size_desktop }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.feature_icon_size_desktop }}px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .ai-hero-feature-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-hero-feature-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.feature_text_size_desktop }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.feature_text_weight }};
    color: {{ block.settings.feature_text_color }};
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .ai-hero-buttons-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: {{ block.settings.buttons_gap }}px;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.buttons_spacing_desktop }}px;
  }

  .ai-hero-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: {{ block.settings.button_padding_vertical }}px {{ block.settings.button_padding_horizontal }}px;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.button_text_size_desktop }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.button_text_weight }};
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.button_border_radius }}px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: none;
  }

  .ai-hero-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}:focus {
    outline: 2px solid;
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .ai-hero-button-1-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_1_bg_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_1_text_color }};
  }

  .ai-hero-button-1-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_1_bg_hover_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_1_text_hover_color }};
  }

  .ai-hero-button-1-{{ ai_gen_id }}:focus {
    outline-color: {{ block.settings.button_1_bg_color }};
  }

  .ai-hero-button-2-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_2_bg_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_2_text_color }};
  }

  .ai-hero-button-2-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_2_bg_hover_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_2_text_hover_color }};
  }

  .ai-hero-button-2-{{ ai_gen_id }}:focus {
    outline-color: {{ block.settings.button_2_bg_color }};
  }

  .ai-hero-info-blocks-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: {{ block.settings.info_blocks_gap }}px;
  }

  .ai-hero-info-block-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .ai-hero-info-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: {{ block.settings.info_icon_size_desktop }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.info_icon_size_desktop }}px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .ai-hero-info-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-hero-info-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .ai-hero-info-label-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.info_label_size_desktop }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.info_label_weight }};
    color: {{ block.settings.info_label_color }};
  }

  .ai-hero-info-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.info_text_size_desktop }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.info_text_weight }};
    color: {{ block.settings.info_text_color }};
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-hero-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: {{ block.settings.content_image_gap_mobile }}px;
    }

    .ai-hero-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: 100%;
      padding-top: {{ block.settings.content_padding_top_mobile }}px;
      padding-bottom: {{ block.settings.content_padding_bottom_mobile }}px;
      padding-left: {{ block.settings.content_padding_horizontal_mobile }}px;
      padding-right: {{ block.settings.content_padding_horizontal_mobile }}px;
    }

    .ai-hero-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: 100%;
      order: 2;
    }

    .ai-hero-headline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.headline_size_mobile }}px;
    }

    .ai-hero-paragraph-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.paragraph_size_mobile }}px;
    }

    .ai-hero-features-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .ai-hero-feature-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: {{ block.settings.feature_icon_size_mobile }}px;
      height: {{ block.settings.feature_icon_size_mobile }}px;
    }

    .ai-hero-feature-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.feature_text_size_mobile }}px;
    }

    .ai-hero-buttons-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex-direction: column;
      width: 100%;
      margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.buttons_spacing_mobile }}px;
    }

    .ai-hero-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: 100%;
      font-size: {{ block.settings.button_text_size_mobile }}px;
    }

    .ai-hero-info-blocks-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex-direction: row;
    }

    .ai-hero-info-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: {{ block.settings.info_icon_size_mobile }}px;
      height: {{ block.settings.info_icon_size_mobile }}px;
    }

    .ai-hero-info-label-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.info_label_size_mobile }}px;
    }

    .ai-hero-info-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.info_text_size_mobile }}px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<hero-section-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-hero-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-hero-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-hero-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <div class="ai-hero-content-inner-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        <h1 class="ai-hero-headline-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {{ block.settings.headline_text }}
          <span class="ai-hero-rotating-word-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <span class="ai-hero-word-{{ ai_gen_id }} active" style="color: {{ block.settings.word_1_color }};">{{ block.settings.word_1 }}</span>
            <span class="ai-hero-word-{{ ai_gen_id }}" style="color: {{ block.settings.word_2_color }};">{{ block.settings.word_2 }}</span>
            <span class="ai-hero-word-{{ ai_gen_id }}" style="color: {{ block.settings.word_3_color }};">{{ block.settings.word_3 }}</span>
            <span class="ai-hero-word-{{ ai_gen_id }}" style="color: {{ block.settings.word_4_color }};">{{ block.settings.word_4 }}</span>
            <span class="ai-hero-word-{{ ai_gen_id }}" style="color: {{ block.settings.word_5_color }};">{{ block.settings.word_5 }}</span>
          </span>
        </h1>

        {% if block.settings.paragraph_text != blank %}
          <p class="ai-hero-paragraph-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.paragraph_text }}</p>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="ai-hero-features-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% if block.settings.feature_1_enabled %}
            <div class="ai-hero-feature-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {% if block.settings.feature_1_icon %}
                <div class="ai-hero-feature-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  <img src="{{ block.settings.feature_1_icon | image_url: width: 100 }}" alt="{{ block.settings.feature_1_text }}" loading="lazy">
                </div>
              {% endif %}
              <span class="ai-hero-feature-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.feature_1_text }}</span>
            </div>
          {% endif %}

          {% if block.settings.feature_2_enabled %}
            <div class="ai-hero-feature-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {% if block.settings.feature_2_icon %}
                <div class="ai-hero-feature-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  <img src="{{ block.settings.feature_2_icon | image_url: width: 100 }}" alt="{{ block.settings.feature_2_text }}" loading="lazy">
                </div>
              {% endif %}
              <span class="ai-hero-feature-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.feature_2_text }}</span>
            </div>
          {% endif %}

          {% if block.settings.feature_3_enabled %}
            <div class="ai-hero-feature-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {% if block.settings.feature_3_icon %}
                <div class="ai-hero-feature-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  <img src="{{ block.settings.feature_3_icon | image_url: width: 100 }}" alt="{{ block.settings.feature_3_text }}" loading="lazy">
                </div>
              {% endif %}
              <span class="ai-hero-feature-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.feature_3_text }}</span>
            </div>
          {% endif %}
        </div>

        <div class="ai-hero-buttons-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% if block.settings.button_1_text != blank %}
            <a href="{{ block.settings.button_1_link }}" class="ai-hero-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-hero-button-1-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {{ block.settings.button_1_text }}
            </a>
          {% endif %}

          {% if block.settings.button_2_text != blank %}
            <a href="{{ block.settings.button_2_link }}" class="ai-hero-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-hero-button-2-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {{ block.settings.button_2_text }}
            </a>
          {% endif %}
        </div>

        <div class="ai-hero-info-blocks-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% if block.settings.info_1_enabled %}
            <div class="ai-hero-info-block-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {% if block.settings.info_1_icon %}
                <div class="ai-hero-info-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  <img src="{{ block.settings.info_1_icon | image_url: width: 100 }}" alt="{{ block.settings.info_1_label }}" loading="lazy">
                </div>
              {% endif %}
              <div class="ai-hero-info-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <div class="ai-hero-info-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.info_1_label }}</div>
                <div class="ai-hero-info-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.info_1_text }}</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          {% endif %}

          {% if block.settings.info_2_enabled %}
            <div class="ai-hero-info-block-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {% if block.settings.info_2_icon %}
                <div class="ai-hero-info-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  <img src="{{ block.settings.info_2_icon | image_url: width: 100 }}" alt="{{ block.settings.info_2_label }}" loading="lazy">
                </div>
              {% endif %}
              <div class="ai-hero-info-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <div class="ai-hero-info-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.info_2_label }}</div>
                <div class="ai-hero-info-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.info_2_text }}</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ai-hero-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% if block.settings.hero_image %}
        <img
          src="{{ block.settings.hero_image | image_url: width: 2000 }}"
          alt="{{ block.settings.hero_image.alt | escape }}"
          loading="lazy"
          width="{{ block.settings.hero_image.width }}"
          height="{{ block.settings.hero_image.height }}"
          class="ai-hero-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
        >
      {% else %}
        <div class="ai-hero-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {{ 'image' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>
</hero-section-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

<script>
  (function() {
    class HeroSection{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
      constructor() {
        super();
        this.currentIndex = 0;
        this.words = [];
        this.intervalId = null;
      }

      connectedCallback() {
        this.words = this.querySelectorAll('.ai-hero-word-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        if (this.words.length > 1) {
          this.startRotation();
        }
      }

      startRotation() {
        this.intervalId = setInterval(() => {
          this.words[this.currentIndex].classList.remove('active');
          this.currentIndex = (this.currentIndex + 1) % this.words.length;
          this.words[this.currentIndex].classList.add('active');
        }, 3000);
      }

      disconnectedCallback() {
        if (this.intervalId) {
          clearInterval(this.intervalId);
        }
      }
    }

    customElements.define('hero-section-{{ ai_gen_id }}', HeroSection{{ ai_gen_id }});
  })();
</script>

